[2026-07-19 18:38:32] [claude-sdk] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019nzw82VAg17DtNvjCA1iqF","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# NEIGHBORHOOD INTEREST FLYER: [Club Name]\n2\t\n3\t**Hey Neighbors!** \n4\t\n5\tAre you interested in **[Club Topic/Interest, e.g., Amateur Radio, Beekeeping, Baking, Gardening]**? \n6\t\n7\tWe are launching an informal, resident-run **[Club Name]** for our block and surrounding blocks! The goal is to bring together local folks who share this interest to swap knowledge, share tools, and build a local network.\n8\t\n9\t---\n10\t\n11\t### 📅 What We'll Do\n12\t*   **[Activity 1, e.g., Monthly porch meetups and node configuration nights]**\n13\t*   **[Activity 2, e.g., Group buys on starter equipment and mesh testing]**\n14\t*   **[Activity 3, e.g., Collaborative street events & range mapping days]**\n15\t\n16\t---\n17\t\n18\t### 💬 How to Connect\n19\tWe are hosting our group coordination on **[Platform, e.g., Signal / Matrix / Discord]**. It's completely free and private.\n20\t\n21\t1.  **Scan the QR Code** below or type in the short-link:\n22\t    \n23\t    ```\n24\t    ┌─────────────────────────┐\n25\t    │                         │\n26\t    │     [ INSERT QR CODE    │\n27\t    │       IMAGE / LINK      │\n28\t    │         HERE ]          │\n29\t    │                         │\n30\t    └─────────────────────────┘\n31\t    ```\n32\t    \n33\t2.  **Short-Link:** `[Insert URL, e.g., https://signal.group/...]`\n34\t3.  **Say Hello:** Jump in the chat and introduce yourself! Let us know what block you're on.\n35\t\n36\t---\n37\t\n38\t### 📍 Meeting Details (First Gathering)\n39\t*   **When:** [Date] at [Time]\n40\t*   **Where:** [Location, e.g., St. Paul Public Library - Highland Park Branch, Room B / [Organizer's Name]'s Front Porch at [Address]]\n41\t*   **Bring:** [What to bring, e.g., Just yourself and an appetite for learning!]\n42\t\n43\t---\n44\t\n45\t*This club is an autonomous interest group facilitated by MNeighbor Alliance (MNA) block routers. Participation is voluntary, non-commercial, and free.*\n46\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"393aa51d-281a-4b41-acea-1abc9b5cff0a","uuid":"9a94bde5-d2ab-43cc-9b1d-0cdbe35c9386","timestamp":"2026-07-19T23:38:32.834Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/c/Users/donno/source/mneighbor-alliance/templates/CLUB_INTEREST_FLYER.md","content":"# NEIGHBORHOOD INTEREST FLYER: [Club Name]\n\n**Hey Neighbors!** \n\nAre you interested in **[Club Topic/Interest, e.g., Amateur Radio, Beekeeping, Baking, Gardening]**? \n\nWe are launching an informal, resident-run **[Club Name]** for our block and surrounding blocks! The goal is to bring together local folks who share this interest to swap knowledge, share tools, and build a local network.\n\n---\n\n### 📅 What We'll Do\n*   **[Activity 1, e.g., Monthly porch meetups and node configuration nights]**\n*   **[Activity 2, e.g., Group buys on starter equipment and mesh testing]**\n*   **[Activity 3, e.g., Collaborative street events & range mapping days]**\n\n---\n\n### 💬 How to Connect\nWe are hosting our group coordination on **[Platform, e.g., Signal / Matrix / Discord]**. It's completely free and private.\n\n1.  **Scan the QR Code** below or type in the short-link:\n    \n    ```\n    ┌─────────────────────────┐\n    │                         │\n    │     [ INSERT QR CODE    │\n    │       IMAGE / LINK      │\n    │         HERE ]          │\n    │                         │\n    └─────────────────────────┘\n    ```\n    \n2.  **Short-Link:** `[Insert URL, e.g., https://signal.group/...]`\n3.  **Say Hello:** Jump in the chat and introduce yourself! Let us know what block you're on.\n\n---\n\n### 📍 Meeting Details (First Gathering)\n*   **When:** [Date] at [Time]\n*   **Where:** [Location, e.g., St. Paul Public Library - Highland Park Branch, Room B / [Organizer's Name]'s Front Porch at [Address]]\n*   **Bring:** [What to bring, e.g., Just yourself and an 