h a start time of 10:00 a.m. on Friday, July 4, 2025\n\n**Community Involvement:**\n- Lex-Ham Crime and Safety Committee Meetings occur on the 3rd Monday of each month at 3:30 PM at Yellowbird Coffee Bar\n\nFor more comprehensive and current information about 2025-2026 programs, I recommend visiting their main programs page at www.lexham.org/lhccprograms or contacting them directly at lexham@lexham.org or (555) 555-5555.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"393aa51d-281a-4b41-acea-1abc9b5cff0a","uuid":"204c220d-ac65-43af-8039-c3161be9379f","timestamp":"2026-07-19T23:42:04.684Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Lexington-Hamline Community Council LHCC programs 2025 2026","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01BoRPTJHywdDw1RfvhAsRj2","content":[{"title":"Programs — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/lhccprograms"},{"title":"Donate — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/donate/"},{"title":"A FULL YEAR of music lessons at Walker West! (value $1650) – The Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://lexham.org/product/a-full-year-of-music-lessons-at-walker-west/"},{"title":"Contact — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/contact/"},{"title":"Portland 4th of July Parade & Social — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/calendar/portland-4th-of-july-parade-social"},{"title":"Maps — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/map/"},{"title":"Board of Directors — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/board"},{"title":"Our Store — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://www.lexham.org/our-store"},{"title":"Safety Links – The Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://lexham.org/community/safety-links/"},{"title":"Merch — Lexington-Hamline Community Council","url":"https://ww