[2026-07-19 18:48:29] [claude-sdk] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_011CdCJvq7PS7ZG7JrLHTgg5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012cmuML1SgkmoXHKFpaks6j","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/c/Users/donno/source/mneighbor-alliance/templates/WELCOME_INFO_SHEET.md","content":"# WELCOME TO THE BLOCK\n\n**Hey neighbor!** We're glad you're here.\n\nWe're a group of neighbors on **[Block Name, e.g., 1400 block of Portland Ave]** who host a few casual block gatherings each year — potlucks, music, activities for the kids. No dues, no meetings, just community.\n\n---\n\n### Your Block Leader\n**Name:** [Block Leader Name]\n**Contact:** [Phone or Email — leader's choice]\n\n### Join the Block Chat\nWe coordinate on **Signal** (free, private, no spam):\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────┐\n│                         │\n│     [ INSERT QR CODE    │\n│       FOR SIGNAL        │\n│       GROUP HERE ]      │\n│                         │\n└─────────────────────────┘\n```\n**Short-Link:** [Insert Signal Group URL]\n\n### Next Neighborhood Event\n**What:** [Event Name, e.g., Summer Block Party]\n**When:** [Date] at [Time]\n**Where:** [Location, e.g., 1400 block of Portland Ave]\n\n---\n\n*This block is part of the [Link Name] neighborhood node of MNeighbor Alliance (MNA) — a volunteer-run, non-commercial civic network. Learn more at [MNA Contact Info / Website].*\n\n---\n*(flip over for quick references)*\n\n---\n\n# QUICK REFERENCES\n\n### City of Saint Paul Services\n| Service | Contact |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| **Non-Emergency Citizen Service Line** | 651-266-8989 |\n| **Western District Police (Non-Emergency)** | 651-266-5512 |\n| **Emergency** | 911 |\n| **Snow Emergency Hotline** | 651-266-PLOW (7569) |\n\n### Recycling & Yard Waste\nRamsey County recycling schedule and guidelines:\n**ramseycounty.us/residents/recycling-waste**\n\n### Nearest Community Garden\n**[Garden Name]** — [Location / Cross Streets]\nContact: [Garden Coordinator Name or Email]\n\n### Crime & Safety Committee\n**When:** [Day, e.g., 3rd Wednesday] of each month at [Time]\n**Where:** [Location, e.g., Yellowbird Coffee Bar, 1168 Selby Ave]\nOpen to all residents. No sign-up required.\n\n### Report a Problem\n*   **Potholes, streetlights, graffiti:** Call 651-266-8989 or use the Saint Paul online reporting form.\n*   **Suspicious activity:** Call SPPD non-emergency at 651-266-5512.\n*   **Noise complaints:** Call 651-291-1111 (after-hours police dispatch).\n\n---\n\n*All variables in [brackets] must be customized for your specific block before printing.*\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":573,"cache_read_input_tokens":42715,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":573},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"393aa51d-281a-4b41-acea-1abc9b5cff0a","uuid":"ae24d114-c29a-47fc-8fbe-c0ce61f61cf9"}
